{"tid":1818063,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"係Amazon買左對波鞋","createTime":"2020-01-09T14:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T06:55:18.000Z","uid":204309,"like":2,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5232a10ebc8026236ea968d3088a59520eec0e57","tid":1818063,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"係一間叫Outdoor deals既供應商買，由amazon配送黎香港<br />\n售價比Amazon自家鋪平差唔多一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又平過波鞋品牌官網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家好驚係假貨，就到再貨我都嚟識分其實<br />\n岩岩上Amazon再睇返件貨，已經無左，變左Amazon自售已經係最平，唔通比我買左，outdoor deals淨係得一件貨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打試過同樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331d62bd3df9180b4389e8a7013b37e4ee9c8ad2","tid":1818063,"uid":160964,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"因為係假貨所以比Amazon ban左"},{"pid":"5b03756cedf66975a86ca69c46c246fa5173b79b","tid":1818063,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"331d62bd3df9180b4389e8a7013b37e4ee9c8ad2","tid":1818063,"uid":160964,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"因為係假貨所以比Amazon ban左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打講真？一個鐘內咁快知